HEADWORD: Keyboard
<hw>Key"board`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The whole
arrangement, or one range, of the <parts>keys</parts>{3} of an organ,
piano, typewriter, etc.; that part of a device containing the
<parts>keys</parts>{3} used to operate it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

